Czechs May Raise Cigarette Tax to Boost Income, Hospodarske Says

-- B y   P e t e r   L a c a
-- 
2011-07-21T06:26:58Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-21/czechs-may-raise-cigarette-tax-to-boost-income-hospodarske-says.html
The Czech Health Ministry may
propose an increase in the excise tax on cigarettes,  Hospodarske
Noviny  reported, citing Jan Ruzicka, head of the minister’s
office.  The ministry wants the additional revenue to compensate for
some of the government’s austerity measures in health care, the
newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Peter Laca in Prague at 
 placa@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Balazs Penz at 
 bpenz@bloomberg.net  